## To ls0 (x: Word64) -> Word64:
    Return rotr(x, 1) xor rotr(x, 8) xor word64Shr(x, 7).

## To ls1 (x: Word64) -> Word64:
    Return rotr(x, 19) xor rotr(x, 61) xor word64Shr(x, 6).

## To bs0 (x: Word64) -> Word64:
    Return rotr(x, 28) xor rotr(x, 34) xor rotr(x, 39).

## To bs1 (x: Word64) -> Word64:
    Return rotr(x, 14) xor rotr(x, 18) xor rotr(x, 41).

## To ch (x: Word64) and (y: Word64) and (z: Word64) -> Word64:
    Return word_and(x, y) xor word_and(word_not(x), z).

## To maj (x: Word64) and (y: Word64) and (z: Word64) -> Word64:
    Return word_and(x, y) xor word_and(x, z) xor word_and(y, z).

## To sha512Compress (state: Seq of Word64) and (m: Seq of Word64) and (kk: Seq of Word64) -> Seq of Word64:
    Let mutable sched be a new Seq of Word64.
    Repeat for x in m:
        Push x to sched.
    Repeat for t from 16 to 79:
        Let s0 be ls0(item (t - 14) of sched).
        Let s1 be ls1(item (t - 1) of sched).
        Let nw be s1 + (item (t - 6) of sched) + s0 + (item (t - 15) of sched).
        Push nw to sched.
    Let mutable a be item 1 of state.
    Let mutable b be item 2 of state.
    Let mutable c be item 3 of state.
    Let mutable d be item 4 of state.
    Let mutable e be item 5 of state.
    Let mutable f be item 6 of state.
    Let mutable g be item 7 of state.
    Let mutable h be item 8 of state.
    Repeat for t from 0 to 79:
        Let t1 be h + bs1(e) + ch(e, f, g) + (item (t + 1) of kk) + (item (t + 1) of sched).
        Let t2 be bs0(a) + maj(a, b, c).
        Set h to g.
        Set g to f.
        Set f to e.
        Set e to d + t1.
        Set d to c.
        Set c to b.
        Set b to a.
        Set a to t1 + t2.
    Let mutable out be a new Seq of Word64.
    Push (item 1 of state) + a to out.
    Push (item 2 of state) + b to out.
    Push (item 3 of state) + c to out.
    Push (item 4 of state) + d to out.
    Push (item 5 of state) + e to out.
    Push (item 6 of state) + f to out.
    Push (item 7 of state) + g to out.
    Push (item 8 of state) + h to out.
    Return out.

## Main
    Let mutable state be a new Seq of Word64.
    Push word64(0x6a09e667f3bcc908) to state.
    Push word64(0xbb67ae8584caa73b) to state.
    Push word64(0x3c6ef372fe94f82b) to state.
    Push word64(0xa54ff53a5f1d36f1) to state.
    Push word64(0x510e527fade682d1) to state.
    Push word64(0x9b05688c2b3e6c1f) to state.
    Push word64(0x1f83d9abfb41bd6b) to state.
    Push word64(0x5be0cd19137e2179) to state.
    Let mutable m be a new Seq of Word64.
    Push word64(0x6162638000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(0x0000000000000000) to m.
    Push word64(24) to m.
    Let kk be sha512K().
    Let result be sha512Compress(state, m, kk).
    Repeat for w in result:
        Show intOfWord64(w).
